 Aneka: Manjasoft’s solution for developing, deploying and managing Cloud applications 
 The Aneka based computing cloud is a collection of physical and virtualized resources connected through a network, which are either the Internet or a private intranet.
 
 Architecture:
    It is a Pure Platform as a service Framework.
 
 Feature:
 1) simplify the development of applications (SDK); 
 2) porting existing applications to the Cloud;
 3) monitoring and managing the Aneka Cloud.
  1.middleware for managing and scaling distributed applications 
  2 applications – an extensible set of APIs for developing them 
  
 
 
